nodes.name: glyceraldehyde ferredoxin oxidoreductase
nodes.rxn: D-Glyceraldehyde + H2O + Oxidized ferredoxin <=> D-Glycerate + H+ + Reduced ferredoxin

nodes.name: D-xylulose 5-phosphate D-glyceraldehyde-3-phosphate-lyase (adding phosphate
nodes.rxn: D-Xylulose 5-phosphate + Orthophosphate <=> Acetyl phosphate + D-Glyceraldehyde 3-phosphate + H2O

nodes.name: D-glyceraldehyde:acceptor oxidoreductase (FAD-containing)
nodes.rxn: D-Glyceraldehyde + H2O + Acceptor <=> D-Glycerate + Reduced acceptor

nodes.name: D-glyceraldehyde:NADP+ oxidoreductase
nodes.rxn: D-Glyceraldehyde + NADP+ + H2O <=> D-Glycerate + NADPH + H+
